reviews.text: Great place for shopping and dining. The lifts to the parking lot, however, are always full. Waiting for the lifts can take 15 minutes or more during rush hours.
More shops than I had time to visit. Something for everyone. Very clean and tidy too!
A lovely ppace fir eating and shopping.(⌐■-■)

Local shopping mall with many shopping outlets. Restaurants and Fast food places, open air garden for
gatherings. Great location - walk bridge connected to Kwai Fong MTR station  Kowloon Hong Kong.
SHK Propoerties has done a good job in renovating the mall, transforming it into a modern and chic place to shop & dine regularly.

reviews.text: 直得一試，反而杯咖啡有驚喜

Min. $60 per person if you want to dine in. 
Somehow the creme brulee served in room temperature and THIS IS NOT HOW CREME BRULEE TASTES LIKE. Only come if you want to enjoy overpriced cake served by monotone unenthusiatic workers.
杯茶還好。甜點十分差的。店員態度亦是。一定不會再去。
蛋糕，比預期中要梗和乾一點，咖啡合格。可能葵芳區，比平時尖沙咀區，閒閒地都過百元，算抵食。
